{
  "texts": [
    "It can also take a large amount of feedback from multiple reviewers and distill it down to a summary that can be easily digested by the author.",
    "Furthermore, it can underpin a transparent and streamlined feedback system that encourages students to engage with their assessments critically, assessing whether to act on an item of feedback.",
    "AI can support instructor oversight of the peer assessment process by providing a dashboard of analytics, highlighting trends, flagging potential issues and suggesting areas for improvement.",
    "This can empower instructors to steer the assessment process more effectively, ensuring that it aligns with educational objectives and standards.",
    "In addition, AI can swiftly identify reviews that deviate from established norms or exhibit signs of bias, facilitating prompt intervention."
  ]
}